<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
As interested in this server as I am, I see 2 things... 1) Bind for casters only in cities?  Just doesn't make sense...  2) I know it's not dubbed *roleplay* server, but PvE everywhere?  One of the great drawbacks of a *blue* server is ... you play a lvl 30 character (doesn't really matter what class) and a lvl 12 is REALLY being annoying outside a city guard's watchful eye... bye bye lvl 12 ... make it PvP outside cities, maybe even outside *newbie* zones (ie Nek, EC, Gfay (though they can have some of the MOST annoying people), Steamfont, QHills, et cetera), but also in relation to this alignment (a Paladin killing another Paladin? I think no, but that necromancer over there on the other hand....)<P>But otherwise, I am looking forward to this new server, and hope it pans out well...looks not too shabby thus far..<P>Be well<P>Java
</FONT>
