I agree. TLC is a dumb idea on such a server. Actually, any server. I can possibly see the use for TLC on 'some' items, but its gonna do more harm than good for what I can forsee. ie: Quillmane's cloak needed for Mage epic. If I'm lv 57 and need that cloak for my epic, how do I get it with it NOT being trivial? It will be a major hassle, and cause a lot of problems, and frustrate a lot of people into quitting. <BR>The bind point thing is another factor. What does this accomplish? It doesn't make a whole lot of sense IMO. Who knows, maybe in 'Beta' they'll realize some of these things.<BR>PvE. I'm not entirely against that, but still not very RPish. I mean, if you're going for roleplaying, that should mean you can play your role. If I'm a rogue looking to slit someone's throat for a few coins, then more power to me. But I can kinda see the reasoning behind that. Just my 2 cents.
