k, I was extremely opposed to TLC being implemented on the current servers. That being said, I LOVE this idea. A new server, new rule set, and a new way to play that discourages the kind of play that makes EQ, in some situations, tolerable at best. I for one will be starting a char on this server as soon as it comes out. <P>Now you guys (Verant) are using your heads! Let good enough alone on the old servers and implement a new and (dare I say) improved rule set on a new server. It's a win win.<P>The servers not even up and it's already working. Just look at all the negative responses so far. This rule set is sure to keep the dewds and pg'ers out.<P>Wohoooo! There's hope yet!<P>Cadfael
