I had to post again after reading some things people posted...<P>First .. I do believe they said they would be limiting shout range, et cetera as well in the past, therefore making it uneffective for auctioning, and really, do you NEED to auction outside a city? really, it's pretty annoying sometimes to see them outside those zones, sometimes useful, but really, from a RP perspective should you even be able to auction at ALL????  no..this  IMO, is fair<P>Trivial Loot Code...they said most things will no longer be no drop...this means  (using previous example from someone) Quillmane's cloak wuold be PURCHASABLE..this means 1 of 2 things, you start your epic at the level you can camp it's lowest piece (duh), or you shell out the plat for it...<P>The no binds outside cities for casters..I saw someone say what I too felt..lessen our xp loss on death then, this is only affecting casters, and in NO way enhances the roleplay effects of the game, it makes things exponentially more difficult in fact, and does NOTHING to melee's, except make them wait longer to get bodies...<P>One character per server...I agree there with VI too, sorry, play the class you are best at, honestly, this server for RP purposes, is unlikely to attract or get *n00bs*...you already probably have a feel for the game mechanics, now play ONE toon you like/love...<P>languages ... /shrug  .. you wanna know 'em, spend the time<P>Now rarely do I have something negative to say to anyone posting, but I wanted to address Vonhase...WAKE THE f&^% up boy... PvE Duelling doesn't work, even if you are all /role all the time, you con someone and they're red on you..99% will NOT /duel you, you get a /decline...in fact, I bet you're one of those annoying little buggers I would like to blast to oblivion...  the point on RP SHOULD be that the higher levels are given respect (at LEAST begrudging leeway) by the lower levels, on PvE, a lvl 1 can look at someone 20, 30, 50 levels higher and tell them off etc w/ no consequences...make it so you upset me & I can exact revenge ... and then in converse, you can work yourself up and come back for me =) but PvE just won't cut it there...<P>just my 2 cp<P>Java
